---
title: Chorizo, Sweet Potato and Chipotle Black Bean Chorizo Tostadas with Rocket Tomato Salad and Greek Style Salad Cheese
description: Looking for a quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Chorizo, Sweet Potato and Chipotle Black Bean Chorizo Tostadas in just 20-25 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
